history.text: Hello, how are you today?
Hello, I'm fine and you?
I'm great thanks. Are you familiar with the movie, Catch me if you can?
I'm not sure, is iit
A magician movie?
It came out in 2002. Oh, no you're thinking of Now You See Me
Oh ok
Catch me if you can is much older, it stars Leonardo Dicaprio and Tom Hanks.
Ok, no I'm not familiar with that movie
What genre is it?
Oh ok. It is a really great crime biography about an actual criminal that was able to fool police for years.
Wow, that sounds interesting

It definitely is. I normally don't mean it when I tell people they should watch a movie on these hits, but this time, I mean it. Leo plays the criminal, and Tom Hanks plays the one detective that refuses to let him get away.
They eventually develop a friendship with one another because over the years they get so used to the cat and mouse game.
Oh wow, I have to look that up
Both are great actors so I know the movie is well done
Definitely check it out. It also has Christopher Walken in it and he plays Leo's dad.
Ok, cool
It's a fun movie all around. Beautiful scenery, pretty exciting scenes
Awesome. Are you a fan of Decaprio and Hanks?
And if you liked the movie Now You See Me, it's actually very much like that. Has an Oceans 11 vibe, where you keep wondering how he's going to get away with it.
Yea I don't think I've ever seen a bad movie from either of them.
Interesting
I really loved Leo in Inception and Gangs of New York.
I loved both oceans 11 and now you see me
Then I definitely think you will enjoy this movie.
I won't give away the ending, but it is very unique.
I believe I've seen inception but not gangs of New York
Gangs of New York was great, but very violent.
I will definitely search for it this weekend
The departed was also a really great movie with leonardo dicaprio and Jack nicholson
Well, it's been a pleasure talking to you. I hope you enjoy it!
Have a great day!

uid1response.feedback: The other user persuaded me to see the movie this weekend without giving away the ending. I am truly interested in seeing the movie after chatting with the other user.
